{
  "stem": "4670.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the girls in my class were my friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In fact, later, there were two reunions in the United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was so excited meeting friends that I hadn't seen for over 50 years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was pretty good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I liked her very much and I really thought she was my closest friend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her name was Margot Hesse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she was a disappointment to me at a very unexpected time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was when Hitler had already come to power.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But first, I must-- just must mention before we come to her, a little bit about during the Hitler period.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we had moved to the-- a lot of things were changing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had moved to Chernivtsi and my parents had talked about the inflation and where the money was printed almost daily.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Their money was worthless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And people were unhappy, and suddenly there were many different political parties.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the-- it was called Nationalsozialistische Party, was one of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it didn't seem to be anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, my parents' friends, they laughed it off as a joke.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, there was a-- in the early '20s, there was a joke going around-- I would say it was around 1928, when Hitler was just beginning-- it was the greeting Heil Hitler, which later was the only greeting around in Germany.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The joke was 'Heil' also means heal, which is the same thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In other words, heil the conqueror, but it's also another way of saying heil is healing someone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the joke would be, when someone would say Heil Hitler, and the answer would be why, is he sick.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it seems not an American kind of joke, but for Germans, at that time, they thought it was funny.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
